data.description: MUST SEE, like new, 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home on a grassy corner lot in Griffith Park with great living space. Enter thru your covered porch surrounded by stone accents and into your open main living space with luxury vinyl plank flooring. Enjoy entertaining in this open concept within your sunny dining space, great room, and kitchen. Kitchen features granite countertops and custom backsplash. Main level office space as an added bonus. Upper level features all your bedrooms, including the primary suite with bath featuring double vanities & oversized standup shower. Wonderful covered back patio for enjoying those Carolina evenings. Close to shopping, dining, hospitals, highways and more. Come visit your new home today! Agent related to seller!
